My city is big. It has many different kinds of people. We live in houses or apartments. Some are small. Some are big. They are mixed together with businesses and stores. Some stores are well-known. Others are small and special. They are like a treasure hunt to find them.

I see many people in my neighborhood. They are from different places. Some are gay. Some are Jewish. Some are from other countries. They all live together in the same area. There are also parks for people to play in. I see many families with young children in these parks.

My neighborhood is not very quiet. There are many things to see and do. We have Korea town, China town, and other places like that. They are not very far away. But it can take a long time to get there because of traffic. It is a big problem. Many people do not walk anywhere. They drive their cars. This makes traffic even worse.

The city is building many new buildings. They are big and have many apartments. Some people are happy about this. Others are not. They do not want more people and cars in the city.

I know my neighbors a little bit. We are not very close. When I was a child, I played with my friends in the neighborhood. We had fun together.

My neighborhood is interesting. It has mostly single-family houses. Some houses have been divided into two homes, connected together. My house has a small yard in front and a small driveway on one side. Most houses look like they did a long time ago. They remind people of a time when living in the suburbs was a dream for Americans. This dream seemed to be for everyone, but now it is changing. My neighborhood and others like it still exist. They still show that the dream is still alive. People are holding onto it as best they can.

People are not as happy as they used to be. The yards are not as nice as they used to be. But there are still cars in every driveway. Children still play outside. They think the world is all they need to be happy. A public school has been here for almost 90 years. It still looks to the future for the young people. It also makes older people remember the past. There are a few churches, but they are not very full. The basketball courts are always busy. All houses look different, but they feel the same.

There is a big store called Super A. It is owned by a large family from Yemen. They may be the only Arab family in the neighborhood. Most people in the neighborhood are African American. The streets are wide, and children play football. They stop playing when cars pass by. Many people have lived in the neighborhood for a long time. They can tell stories about the past when everyone knew each other.

There was a karate school, but it is now a pharmacy. This is because people think medicine can make everything better. A small movie theater shows old movies at a lower price. It is not popular with young people because it does not show new movies. Older people like it because it is a good place to go out without the young people. There is a highway that goes through our town. The entrance and exit are in the next town. People wanted to put an exit in our town, but older people said it would ruin the town. They convinced the city council to say no.

A new high school is being built, and we are choosing a mascot for our town. I think a cyborg with a country accent and a cabin would be a good symbol for our town.

You might not notice it at first. It's a residential area behind a shopping strip. People do not think there are homes here that most people would want to live in. But if you go behind the old, abandoned Whole Foods and walk to the back, you will find a community. There are buildings that serve as homes, one next to the other. These buildings are like small houses that are connected together.

Some of these buildings have been in the news for problems. We will not talk about those buildings too much. But the buildings next to those are a different world. Almost no one in the area knows about them.

Across from these buildings is a small college. It is a quiet place with a few buildings. Students go there to learn. They come and go, drinking coffee and yawning. The gates of the college open slowly to let them in. The people who drive by are a little angry that the students are causing traffic.

The road splits into another road. There is a park on one side and a place that helps people who broke their bones. The place has nice furniture outside and a big fan that moves the air.

Children play in the park. They are happy and healthy. There are flowers by the road. Bees fly around them. Old people walk their dogs on a path in the park. They look at the teenagers on skateboards and the girls talking about boys and YouTube.

There is a place that serves sushi in a shopping area near the park. It is not very busy. There is a store that sells things for pools and a place that does nails. You can buy a pool and get a manicure at the same time. There is a place that sells frozen yogurt. People eat it while they do tricks on their skateboards.

The area is a part of America. It is a piece of history in a quiet part of the south. Not much changes here, not even time.

We drove past fields of corn that stretched as far as the eye could see. "Where are we?" she asked. "This is it," I said. I knew she would be surprised by the open space. She was from a town where the grocery store was close to her house. She had never seen so much empty land.

I told her about growing up in rural Ohio. She finally understood who I was and where I came from. We drove on a two-lane road. We passed a big hole in the ground filled with water. After that, we came to a small area where people live. The houses are made of brick and stucco. Each house has a big yard. People like to take care of their yards. In the spring, many flowers grow, and the trees change with the seasons. The driveways have nice cars. They shine in the sunlight after they are washed.

As we drove, my neighbor was outside. He was friendly. He was mowing his lawn and singing. Everyone likes him. He is a good person with a special past. He used to be a doctor. He is older now and not as quick-witted as he used to be. He likes to ride his lawn mower and listen to its sound.

We finally came to my house. There are geese in the yard, and our dog chases them. There is a stream in the back. You can hear the water, the frogs, and the cows from the farms. Across a bridge made of wood, there is a special area with trees, herbs, and flowers that grow on their own. This is where I spent most of my childhood. I built forts in the trees and played with my friends. In the winter, the yard is empty and quiet. The trees look like skeletons. Sometimes it snows, and the yard becomes a winter wonderland. My sister and I would make snowmen and fight with snowballs. We built forts to store our snowballs. We played in our own little world and didn't worry about anything.

Portland, Oregon is a city that loves being different. The city's unofficial message is "Keep Portland Weird." Some people think this means keeping the city how it was in the 1990s and early 2000s. That was a time when Portland was not well-known and less expensive. Many creative and unique groups lived there. To others, "Keep Portland Weird" means come to the city and be accepted as different. Even though many people from California have moved here, and many new buildings are being built, Portland is still a strange and accepting place. We are not always accepting, but we accept things that others do not. We have modern things like everyone else, but we do not take things too seriously.

In my neighborhood, you can see many colorful houses and home gardens with flowers, herbs, and vegetables. In the summer, you can find free boxes on the street. These are boxes with things people are giving away. You can find clothes, books, and even other things. Sometimes you can find something special. That is what Portland is all about to me. But I am just one person, and there are many others like me. Some people I live with would never take things from the street. They go to goat yoga or watch soccer games.

Portland has people who love many things. Some people have big dreams, but they spend too much time at the bar. Portland has problems like many cities. We have a problem with drugs. Many of these problems are about mental health. We have a lot of rain and cloudy skies, which can be hard to deal with. We also have a problem with homelessness. Many people come to Portland for help, but we do not have enough services. The people who have homes do not know what to do about this problem. They feel both sad and angry.

The mountains are always there. They stand in the north, watching the sun rise and set. They do not move or change. They are strong and steady. When I am busy or stressed, they remind me to stop and look at them. They give me strength to keep going. I first saw the mountains when I started college. They were near our campus. The college has many beautiful things, but the mountains are special. I like the buildings, ponds, and trees on campus. But the mountains are the most important.

The town is also nice. There are many cafes where I studied and had coffee. You can walk or take a bus to the town center. It's old and colorful. The buildings are made of bricks that are fading. It's like a different world. But then you can go back to the quiet town and feel peaceful. This town has two different feelings. You can feel happy and busy in the town center. Or you can feel calm in the quiet town. I like this feeling. It's like the town is inviting me to explore.

I have many happy memories in this town. I walked with friends to the park after studying all night. We sat on the swings and talked. I also went to the movie theater with friends. The college gave us tickets. But the town also has sad memories. We all have sad memories in life. The ponds are a good place to think and cry. I sat by the pond when I was feeling lost. I watched the turtles and ducks living their lives. I wondered about my own life and what I wanted to do.

I walked to the main street and saw the sun shining. I looked up and saw the mountains in the distance. They were still there, strong and steady. They reminded me to keep going. They made me feel brave.

Bensonhurst, Brooklyn, is a good place to visit. Getting there is easy. You can use public transportation. Many people use public transportation in New York City. Bensonhurst is a city neighborhood. You will feel like you are in New York City. You will see many Asian stores. Many Asian people have moved to Bensonhurst in the last twenty years. You will see an Asian store almost every block. They sell food and do laundry. People like these stores because the food is good, prices are low, and it is convenient. I live near here. Four Asian supermarkets are near me. You can walk to them in two minutes. This makes it easy to buy food. Bensonhurst is not only Asian people. It is diverse. Many people are immigrants and their families. Many businesses are owned by Asian people. There is a new park near here. It has basketball courts, a soccer field, handball courts, swings, and a water fountain. The park is safe and people of all kinds play there. There are no big company buildings here. Most people live in two-family houses. The people are nice, but some can be loud. You may hear music from cars and people driving fast. If you visit at night, be careful. This neighborhood is safe, but some people can be mean. I was hurt here many years ago. Recently, some people stole packages from homes. People do not clean up after their dogs. You will see dog waste on the street every day. My biggest problem is dog waste on the sidewalk. Be careful and keep your shoes clean!

I live in a place without many sidewalks. My house is located at the top of a steep hill. People call it the "workout hill" because many people jog there. We have no sidewalks on my street, so people walk on the road. The road has some holes, and it can be hard to drive on. Some of the telephone and electric wires around my block look old and broken. It rains and storms often here, so branches and other things hit the wires and cause problems. We need to repair them often. There are many tall evergreen trees everywhere. But people dislike the trees. They want to cut them down because they block the view of the ocean. That's why many houses are built high on the hill with big windows to see the water. It's beautiful at sunset when the water shines and the sky turns orange. But the sky is often cloudy and damp. Moss grows on things like roofs, cars, and railings. I left my car outside for a month, and when I came back, it was covered with moss. It took me three hours to clean it off. We don't have many children in my neighborhood. There is a school nearby, but most people are older and retired. They have dogs instead of kids. It's common to see them in yards or running down the street. If you leave a door or window open, dogs might get in. I once found a dog in my living room and had to chase it out. We also have rabbits. They dig up plants and burrow into yards. My cats like to hunt them. We have many birds: small sparrows, hummingbirds, and sometimes a hawk or eagle comes by until the crows chase it away. There are no stores near my house, but if you walk down to the waterfront, there are some restaurants that serve fresh seafood. We have some rocks by the water where you can throw things. The bay is not very big, but you can see the other side clearly on most days.

I live in a small town in Tennessee. It's near two big roads, so there is some traffic. But overall, it's a quiet neighborhood. Few people move in or out, so we know most of our neighbors. They work in their yards and do daily tasks. In the winter, we sled down a nearby hill.

We live in a house at the corner of our street. So, we see everyone who comes and goes. We notice strange cars. Some neighbors walk for exercise or to walk their dogs. Kids ride their bikes. We work from home. There are four of us: my wife and our two daughters, who are eleven and fourteen years old.

We go outside a lot, even in the rain. We sometimes grill on our back deck. It's nice to smell the barbecue. Every day, we hear lawn mowers from March to October. Our neighborhood was once a forest, so there are many trees and shade. In the fall, we rake and burn leaves. I like the smell of burning leaves, which means fall has arrived.

We don't have much winter, so it feels like a long fall. Our garage is at the back of our house. We use the front door only when someone visits. I like to work in the garage and feel connected to the neighborhood when the garage doors are open. During holidays, it's quiet. But on Thanksgiving and other holidays, we see more cars because families visit from out of town.

Overall, I like living here. If it weren't a through street, it would be perfect.

My neighborhood is in the middle of a desert. It is very dry and brown. You see dirt everywhere. If you have not lived here, you may not understand how it feels to see no green for a long time. When I first moved here in the 1990s, houses were far apart. Now there are more houses. The area looks more like a town every day. But it is not the only place that is changing. Many places are like this.

Most people are friendly here. But like in any town, there are good and bad things. I live near older people. They are nice. The stores here are chain stores like Food for Less and Smart. If you want to buy something special, you have to go somewhere else. There are no stores like Whole Foods here. The main jobs in my town are in construction. Many people work here because the town is still growing and there is much open space to build. I am a drywall and T-bar installer. I like my job.

I like my home because of the animals. People come to the desert for its beauty. The desert is hard to live in, but it is home to many animals. Humans must learn about these animals to live here safely. My family and I like the animals. We have three children and they like catching lizards and bugs. We go outside and try to catch them.

We have some attractions here. Victorville is a good place for families to visit the desert. You can have fun and learn something new. There is an annual event called the San Bernardino County Fair. You should visit during the fair. You can also visit nearby Wrightwood to see the snow and go skiing. If you are interested in the history of the desert, you can visit the Victor Valley Museum. It has many interesting things to see.

My neighborhood is a special place. I live in a college campus. My community is the people who live in my dorm. I also think of the campus as my neighborhood. But, it's not like other neighborhoods.

My neighborhood has houses, people, stores, and parks. Let's talk about the houses first. There are three kinds of houses here. First, there are apartments. They have 2-4 people in each room. There are 4-6 rooms on each floor. Each building has 2 floors and 20 people.

Then, there are houses that people can rent. These houses are usually 2-4 bedrooms. But there are not many of them because they are not very useful. Finally, there are dorm rooms. These rooms have 2 people sharing a room. They are the most common kind of housing here.

My neighborhood is very diverse. People from all cultures and ages live here. The professional staff live in the houses, and the new students live in dorms. The older students live in apartments.

Let's talk about the stores and parks. My school has many stores. They have food, clothes, and other things. We can buy what we need here. We also have one park. It's a place for everyone to play. The park is clean and safe because everyone in my neighborhood looks after it.

I have lived in this neighborhood for about 10 years. At first, I was unhappy. I came from Riverdale to Stockbridge. I was sad because I missed my old home and my friends. But my mom and dad wanted the best for me and my sister. They moved us to a new home in a better neighborhood. The new neighborhood had a good school and safe streets.

Over time, I made new friends and enemies in school. I did not know my neighbors well, except for Mr. Glen and his family. They are nice people who I like. They are like a second family to me. I remember going to Mr. Glen's wedding. It was fun.

I was happy to see Mr. Glen's wife, Ms. Veda, remove her bandage and throw it. I caught the bandage, but not the flowers. We danced and had a good time. I enjoyed myself with Marsharii, one of Mr. Glen's daughters. I have not seen her since.

The neighborhood is like a maze, but I have a GPS now. I can explore more easily. I have walked around with my friends Kason and Curtis. We play video games and have fun. I also like to go to the park and enjoy nature. It makes me feel calm and peaceful.

I like to practice my balance with sticks I buy from the store. I also bring my wooden sword and have fun. There are basketball and tennis courts in the neighborhood. I used to play tennis with my dad and a man named Mr. Graves. We worked hard, but we had fun.

I have many happy memories in this neighborhood. I am excited to see what the future holds.

My house is near a college where I study. I like living there. There are many apartment buildings, some restaurants and bars. I like going to these places because they are not too expensive. One bar changed its name and is now more expensive, but it's still okay. The people in my neighborhood are nice. They are mostly college students or people with low incomes because the apartments are not very expensive. There are many children near my house. There is a school for them within walking distance. I do not know my neighbors well. They smoke a lot of marijuana. The manager of my building put a machine that makes the air smell good near their door. My boyfriend and I think this is funny. It's like they are being scolded.

The buildings around me are old, but the inside might be new. Down the street, there are new apartments, but I don't like them. They are cheaply made and the rent is high. I think this is unfair. The people who live in these apartments are rich because they are near the college. The city gives them money to make the area look nice. The road near my house was fixed last summer. Now there is a nice sidewalk and grass on the sides of the road. But my apartment building has many trees. Some of them were cut down, so there are stumps left. There are more trees near my house than on the street behind me. Behind my building, there are trees and another apartment complex.

I live on 42nd Street. The street behind me is 43rd Street. It's not as nice. The sidewalk is bad and falling apart. The buildings look old and tired. There are many trees on this street to hide how bad the buildings look. There have been problems with crime in my area, mostly in one apartment complex. But I think I like where I live. I can afford it, and it's close to the university. There is a store and a downtown area near my house that I can get to easily by bus.

My neighborhood is made up of houses on a circular street. The houses are close together. They look like separate houses, but they are really connected. They are painted yellow with white porches and green metal roofs. Most people are friends with each other. We stand on the end of the street some evenings and talk while the children play with toys, draw with chalk or fly kites. This is nice in a world with many machines and computers. It is like going back in time. We are near fields and trees with blue skies and white clouds. But this season, we have had warning signs for tornadoes. For the first time, we heard real tornado sirens last night. We went to a safe place. I was in my bathtub with my small dog and a few pillows. My big dog was in the living room, barking nervously. The neighborhood was quiet, except for the sound of big hail on the ground. After the storm, the road was hot and steaming. It went from 92 to 75 degrees in a short time. The hail melted on the road. The sun came out, and it started to rain. I saw a double rainbow in the sky. I quickly took pictures with my camera. The streets were quiet for a while. Then people came home from wherever they were. It was business as usual - moms and children outside while dinner cooked. I like my neighborhood. I moved here from New Hampshire to North Carolina. I like the way people speak here. I have a two-bedroom and two-bathroom apartment. But all the houses look the same on the outside. The apartments are not the same on the inside. Some are small. I like to walk in the big field behind my house. I go to the pond that is not for swimming. I have seen deer and in the morning, I hear a big frog singing. It is a nice place to live near the city of Charlotte. Every morning, I hear roosters crowing from the farms. It is like living in a small village. We have a donkey in a farm near here that brays in the evening. I was lucky to find this neighborhood.

I moved to this neighborhood when I started eighth grade. It was hard to make friends at first. But I got close to a friend who lives two houses away and another guy on my street. They no longer live here, but I still remember them. Most people who lived here when I moved in are still living here. My neighborhood is like many American suburbs. It has two-story houses. Every weekend, I hear kids playing outside when it's warm. The neighborhood is quiet most days. I have never had problems with my neighbors. You can be alone unless you need help. I have ordered packages online and never had one stolen. I trust my neighbors. A park is near my house. I played basketball, football, and baseball with my friends there. I had a bad memory there when I got hit in the nose playing football. But I have many good memories. Now, I visit the park with my cousin's kids. They are younger and like playing on swings and slides. The park makes me feel nostalgic. My neighborhood is diverse. You can find many kinds of food nearby. In a short distance, you can find Chinese, Indian, Mexican, and Italian restaurants. People often use apps like GrubHub and DoorDash to get food delivered. There are many fast food places, and you can find them in most neighborhoods. There are also many pizza places. We have many stores with everything you need. There are dry cleaners, a Walgreens, a CVS, and a grocery store called Jewel-Osco. Some stores are special, like an Indian store where you can buy Indian food. I like my neighborhood. I feel lucky because some people on social media and the news have bad experiences with their neighbors.

My neighborhood is a small town in South Carolina. It is not very different from other towns in the state. But Johnston is special because it is known as the Peach Capital of the World. This is why you will see a big sign welcoming visitors.

The town is mostly farmland. You will see many peach trees and cows. The houses are far apart. Most are two stories high with metal roofs or gray shingles. The houses are not near the road. Instead, they are in the fields.

In the center of the town, there is a single traffic light. This is where you can find a few stores. There is a Chinese restaurant called Hong Kong. There is also a Mexican restaurant called Fiesta. There is a small burger place called Gary's. There used to be a pizzeria, but it closed.

There is a small pharmacy called Maxwell and Halford Drug. They sell Cherry Coca-Cola. There is a small grocery store called IGA. But most people go to a bigger store in another town to buy their food. The most popular store in Johnston is Dollar General. It sells many things and is always busy.

There is a small furniture store called Possibilities Furniture & More. They have been in business for a long time and deliver their furniture. Next to the furniture store, there is a pet groomer called Clark's Cuts and Kennels. They take care of pets and sell things to make them look nice.

There are two small medical offices in the town. One is for doctors and the other is for animals. There is a small school in the town called Johnston Elementary School. But when children get older, they go to school in another town.

There is no park in the town, but they are making a new park. It will be 2.5 acres big and people can use it to have fun. But there is not much to do in Johnston. There are no movie theaters, bowling alleys or playgrounds. It is a small town, but it is nice.

I first heard my place's story on a podcast about people who went missing. It was surprising. Almost every apartment in the area cost over one thousand dollars a month. I had never heard this story before, and neither had my friends. Maybe it is because of the struggle. I know some of my friends cry at night. Life is expensive, but we have learned to save money. You get used to the smell of old toys and old clothes. You smell less as an adult. Some people smoke, and some people get used to things.

There are three thrift stores I can walk to. If I start on one side, I can visit two charity stores, a library, a used bookstore, and a shop with strange things. Downtown is busy. Cars and people fill the streets every day, but you cannot hear it in the thrift stores. It is quiet. It is a good place to spend an afternoon. Every year, more and more people and cars come. It is a growing city. One of the biggest online companies is here. The city is still growing. It reminds me of New York. Everyone is busy with their own goals. People do not ask you many questions. You can be alone and quiet, and people will leave you alone. This is different from the South, where people are more friendly. Here, people do not ask you many questions. You can keep to yourself. The city is lively. The pianist next door and the singers upstairs play music. We have a community. We help each other when we need it. We celebrate birthdays and funerals together. I am lucky to live here. I like most of my neighbors. They treat me well. I try to clean up after myself and share food with them. They do the same for me. It is nice to see them, and I think they enjoy my company.

I live in a big, modern building, but my neighbors make me feel like I did not make a mistake with my life.

I live in a common type of neighborhood. It is called a suburb. Many homes here look the same. They are well taken care of because of a group called the homeowner's association. The homes have small lawns, some pebbles, and short driveways. Some trees are present. Everyone has a two-car garage. The roads are new and in good condition. There are no big holes on the road. The houses are usually one story, but some are two stories. We do not have mailboxes in front of each house. Instead, there is a large box at the end of the street. People use a key to get to their mailbox. There are also big boxes for packages. The homeowner's association is responsible for this.

My house is on the edge of a bigger city. This makes our neighborhood a mix of rural and suburban areas. We have a lot of space. There are community pools that everyone can use. They are well taken care of and locked. There are also walking paths where you can walk your dog or go for a walk. You do not need to go to a park to exercise. Our neighborhood is big enough to walk around and get some exercise. Most of the people who live here are old. Our area is safe, and people look out for each other. Some younger people and middle-aged people also live here.

The city is big, but it feels small. We have many things that people need. For example, we have one big store called a mall. It is not very big, but it has what we need. It takes me 15 minutes to drive to get to important places. When I get there, I can find many stores. We have stores that sell good food and stores that sell things cheap. All in all, my neighborhood is safe and good. We have nice things like pools and paths to walk on. We are not very close to stores, but we can drive to get to any store we want.

I live in a small town in the Midwest. The town is close to a big city. My neighborhood is on the east side of the town. It is not the most wealthy area. The houses are not very expensive. Many people rent or own these houses. They are mostly low-income families. But it is not a bad place. My neighbors are friendly. They say hello to me when I walk outside.

There is some crime in our area. It is a little higher than in other parts of the town. There have been some shootings and a few murders in the last 10 years. But nothing has happened to my family. We have lost a few things from our porch, but that is all.

The town has a big problem. Many people have died from opioid overdoses. This is a big problem all over the United States. We have help for people with addiction. There are centers to help them get better. The townspeople are trying to stop this problem.

Our town has some good things too. My son's school is great. The teachers and staff are excellent. They take care of my son and make sure he is safe. He has a disability, but he does not get bullied. Everyone is very friendly. The school gives food to all students so they do not go hungry. No one has to pay for school things like lunch or supplies.

The town leaders are making our town look better. They are fixing roads and parks. But most of the work is done in the center of the town and the west side. The east side, where I live, is not as nice. People are unhappy about this.

I like living in this town. My neighbors are nice, the school is great, and we have many stores to buy things. Our house is not very expensive, but it is okay. We have lived here for 16 years and we do not want to move.

My neighborhood is special. It is on a hill. Many old buildings are there. People go there. I live in a tall building. It has seven floors. Across the street is an old theater. A few blocks away is a small bar. People go there on warm summer nights. They like to play games and have fun. 

Nearby is a big park. It is a good place to walk and play. The park is surrounded by strong walls. During the cold winter months, homeless people live there. They set up tents in a row. They are warm because they are close together. They can walk to a place where they can wash their bodies.

I like my neighborhood. It is not the beautiful buildings or the old streets that I like. It is the people. People used to live in my neighborhood in a bad way. There was much violence. The government and police came to stop the violence. People remember this. They tell their children and grandchildren about it.

Even though my neighborhood is not perfect, people work hard to keep it clean. They care about their city and their block. They want to make it a good place to live. Some people think it is not safe at night. They say white people should not walk there at night. I think this is a reminder of a bad time. I think it is because people do not understand each other. But I feel safe on my street. People are kind to me. They give me help when I need it. One day, a person gave me money when I was cold and alone. They said I was beautiful and valuable. I like my neighborhood because of the people. It is home for me. I feel happy when I walk on the streets at night. People are friendly and kind. They make me feel welcome.

I live in a small town in Michigan. It is far from big cities. We do not have big shopping centers like Wal-mart or Target. There is an Applebee's restaurant, but we have to drive to get there. Our town is near two big lakes. Lake Michigan is one and Lake Charlevoix is the other. Everywhere you look, you can see a place to swim. My home is in a neighborhood with many houses. They are not the same, but they are old and nice. Some are being fixed up. Many houses have basements. You can see the basements from the street. The houses are different colors. Most of them have yards. You can see kids playing on trampolines and swings. Some people grow food in their yards. The houses look like they belong in the middle of America. People work hard to make a living. They often have families or have raised families. You can see kids playing on the streets. People walk dogs and ride bicycles. We know our neighbors. We can tell who belongs here and who does not. We see people grilling outside and say hello. We see people walking their dogs and smile. The lawns are kept nice. People do not leave leaves on the ground. The grass is cut and looks nice. If people have plants, they are cut back. Our neighborhood is not a fancy place, but it is a good place to live. It is quiet and peaceful. It is safe. We have a police station and a jail nearby. The health department is close too. We have a recycling center. People use the services it offers. We have baseball and softball fields. You can hear the people calling the games. Our small airport is nearby. You can hear the planes flying. You can walk to get ice cream from a store near my house. My kids can ride their bicycles to the park, which is a few blocks away. It is a great place to live.
